Post-Match Reflections: Babar Azam: 'We've had some unfinished business since 2019'
Scott Edwards: 'It's a bit disappointing. Firstly, we bowled and fielded well. We thought they were par. We thought we had a good chance at 2 for 120.'
Saud Shakeel: 'I knew I'd be batting No. 5, I tried to improve my shots, attacking options and be brave.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played at Rajiv Gandhi International Stadium, Uppal, Hyderabad
The Player of the Match was Saud Shakeel
Others: The match was a day-night 50-over match
The match was part of the ICC Cricket World Cup 2023-24
